verse = \lyricmode {
  Our God will not keep si -- lent. See, he comes!
Fire goes be -- fore him and all things con -- sumes;
fierce -- ly a tem -- pest round a -- bout him swirls.
His sum -- mons he at his cre -- a -- tion hurls;
the heavens a -- bove and earth be -- low shall hear him:
he comes to judge his peo -- ple. May all fear him!
}
